{"tid":847954,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"樓下大快活有個阿姐，幾正","createTime":"2018-10-04T14:19:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-04T16:02:48.000Z","uid":58316,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f0f1e50f1d7dac954afaee240f4ead08917b8f23","tid":847954,"uid":58316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T14:19:06.000Z","msg":"目測做左五六年<br />\n個陣落去食最平早餐<br />\n心諗點解會有條正女執檯抹櫈<br />\n大陸人<br />\n但真心覺得正<br />\n富貴相<br />\n齋睇樣<br />\n似銀行高層<br />\n上報紙推銷乜pay物pay個d<br />\n真係好靚<br />\n唔知有冇仔女<br />\n而家冇食大快活<br />\n戒左出街食<br />\n但佢仲係度做<br />\n咁耐都冇職升<br />\nd盤真係好重<br />\n又要抹人地倒瀉d奶茶汽水<br />\n唉咁辛苦為乜<br />\n揾個幾廿蚊個鐘<br />\n真係命<br />\n如果我係富家子<br />\n一早溝左佢<br />\n畀一千幾百萬佢老公離婚<br />\n再嫁俾我<br />\n可惜燒味助理仲揾得多過我"},{"pid":"329373170e707945bd1b31a039f4c692378d4bb3","tid":847954,"uid":38642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T14:19:21.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"8a86fe0dbe2d3bcc64f9928d8b17cc0fd4d896f7","tid":847954,"uid":208180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T14:20:29.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"f340bfbced97d946630c0be5c3bf6d122abb2860","tid":847954,"uid":26429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T14:21:08.000Z","msg":"大快活阿姐都要數? 直接屌樓主老母啦"},{"pid":"ddd175074460599ac4db609292056dbba44b455c","tid":847954,"uid":67779,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"329373170e707945bd1b31a039f4c692378d4bb3","tid":847954,"uid":38642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T14:19:21.000Z","msg":"10"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T14:21:14.000Z","msg":"數乜撚啫<br />\n伯母，打攪哂"},{"pid":"7cec0aaece3b12eb4d3fc1a25f27418b0963ec96","tid":847954,"uid":40679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T14:21:23.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"ada79bdb4bbf2790526614dd3988889d00a12033","tid":847954,"uid":146514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"329373170e707945bd1b31a039f4c692378d4bb3","tid":847954,"uid":38642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"